#: ../../install.rst:504
msgid "The |trueos| installer supports multiple ZFS configurations:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../install.rst:506
msgid "**mirror:** Requires a minimum of 2 disks."
msgstr ""

#: ../../install.rst:508
msgid ""
"**RAIDZ1:** Requires a minimum of 3 disks. For best performance, a maximum "
"of 9 disks is recommended."
msgstr ""

#: ../../install.rst:511
msgid ""
"**RAIDZ2:** Requires a minimum of 4 disks. For best performance, a maximum "
"of 10 disks is recommended."
msgstr ""

#: ../../install.rst:514
msgid ""
"**RAIDZ3:** Requires a minimum of 5 disks. For best performance, a maximum "
"of 11 disks is recommended."
msgstr ""

#: ../../install.rst:517
msgid "**stripe:** Requires a minimum of 2 disks."
msgstr ""

#: ../../install.rst:519
msgid ""
"A stripe does NOT provide ANY redundancy. If any disk fails in a stripe, all"
" data in the pool is lost!"
msgstr ""

#: ../../install.rst:522
msgid ""
"The installer will not allow a configuration choice in which the system does"
" not meet the minimum number of disks required by the configuration. When "
"selecting a configuration, a message will indicate how many more disks are "
"required."
