"will not guess and which the user can remember. Passphrases are case-"
"sensitive and can contain spaces. The passphrase should be memorable to the "
"user, such as a line from a song or piece of literature, but hard to guess "
"so people who know the user can not guess the passphrase."
msgstr ""

#: ../../install.rst:846
msgid ""
